{"tid":2218409,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗拒見家屬 反責泛民嘥時間","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:47:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc0c2600c263224a1537cc63a564f0f05b92abc","tid":2218409,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/R4LY7CQZVBBPXAPAL6PSGBUTCA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FR4LY7CQZVBBPXAPAL6PSGBUTCA%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu3qIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=c7a89a9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FR4LY7CQZVBBPXAPAL6PSGBUTCA%2F&h=9ea90650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/R4LY7CQZVBBPXAPAL6PSGBUTCA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n張建宗拒見家屬 反責泛民嘥時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AXa5US5ca5Qju3Vepf49ChzeNjY=/1161x912/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PGYUG5G2O5FTBHQE6I5WAQ4EXU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAXa5US5ca5Qju3Vepf49ChzeNjY%3D%2F1161x912%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPGYUG5G2O5FTBHQE6I5WAQ4EXU.gif&h=5043f69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■張建宗在立法會上被民主派議員包圍，要求跟進12名港人情況。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港青涉偷渡到台灣但遭內地截獲並扣押逾一個月，特區政府未有應家屬要求提供適切援助，被捕人至今音訊全無。政務司長張建宗昨出席立法會財委會，會前多名民主派議員上前向張請願，促張建宗會見12港人家屬，並在會上繼續追問此事。張建宗回應議員質詢時，拒絕與12港人家屬會面，並批評議員在會上追問12港人的問題是「離題萬丈、浪費時間」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：再多一人被頒拘捕令<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拒回應任何訴求<br />\n<br />\n張建宗昨抵達立法會時被民主派議員包圍，議員舉起標語並高叫口號，要求港府派員到深圳了解被拘留12名港人的情況，並要求張建宗親自與家屬會面，示威期間議員與立法會保安推撞，張建宗由會議室退避至官員休息室，又走到另一會議室暫避。在民主派議員圍堵下，張建宗拒回應任何訴求，僅稱會考慮議員的意見，又指入境處已經與家屬有聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n..........................................張建宗只如錄音機般說，入境處和駐粵辦已向內地轉達家屬要求，並稱入境處已與家屬會面，他更批議員重複提問有關12港人的問題是浪費時間。民主黨鄺俊宇再要求張建宗與12港青家屬會面，張建宗再次逃避問題，稱會議是談紓困扶貧，若再討論12港人的問題是「離題萬丈」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rtPFnIRQVRL1juuIf7RlSRJSvIA=/1183x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XXQLGLEJYRGHJFYDJK73ASGK4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrtPFnIRQVRL1juuIf7RlSRJSvIA%3D%2F1183x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXXQLGLEJYRGHJFYDJK73ASGK4E.jpg&h=d1eac60b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被扣留人士李宇軒的妹妹為兄長開設fb專頁，尋求外界關注。《香港獨立媒體》提供圖片"},{"pid":"9c4fdef5b4e30d09965cb9149d41470cfe42775a","tid":2218409,"uid":267791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}